{"tid":2244820,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當奴侵：很久沒與習近平通話　因不想與對方傾談","createTime":"2020-10-15T18:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T19:00:14.000Z","uid":20933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59ca4d071b9eeafc09426511898c53dd05345b2f","tid":2244820,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T18:36:03.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普接受霍士財經頻道訪問，指由於憂慮中國處理新型冠狀病毒疫情的手法，他已有一段時間沒有與國家主席習近平通話，因為他不想與對方傾談。特朗普又指，中國繼續按照一月達成的中美首階段貿易協議，採購美國商品。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普近月一再指責中國，任由新型冠狀病毒擴散到其他國家，並多度以「中國病毒」稱呼這種病毒。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2361802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2361802&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=51c3749e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2361802</a>"},{"pid":"a5904de05ff7338d37d2f4efdcb6e441c3a41548","tid":2244820,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"侵侵好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006a2087cd3e1b94f9e9f1913b31f12d7ce22fb7","tid":2244820,"uid":19817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T18:55:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇清楚兩黨同左媒形勢，就應該做實事, 背水一戰"},{"pid":"b2038ad4617c084df5cdbe8faef0950f84a74375","tid":2244820,"uid":19817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2244825/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n睇清楚兩黨同左媒形勢，就應該做實事, 背水一戰"},{"pid":"db2d8268c0b1cbb34e6cf8d37cc5229b468bee8c","tid":2244820,"uid":344625,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"咁宣戰未"}]}